data.description: This property is a promising gem! It's a three-bedroom, one-and-a-half-bathroom brick ranch home nestled in the highly coveted Pebblebrook High School district. This house boasts a sizable, level lot, complete with a fenced backyard and storage buildings. What's particularly exciting is the potential it holds Co it's a canvas waiting for someone to transform it into their dream home! Its convenient location is a major plus, with easy access to Austell, Mableton, Powder Springs, and Marietta, making commuting or exploring the area a breeze. Furthermore, its proximity to schools, shopping centers, and dining spots adds an extra layer of convenience and appeal. With a bit of vision and creativity, this property could easily become the perfect home for someone seeking a blend of comfort, potential, and accessibility. Welcome home!
